-----

.. [#at] The RS232, RS485, and CAN channels may be customized to the following arrangement:

        + 2 x RS232, 2 x RS485, 1 x CAN (Default)
        + 2 x RS232, 1 x RS485, 2 x CAN
        + 4 x RS232, 0 x RS485, 1 x CAN
        + 0 x RS232, 4 x RS485, 1 x CAN
        + 0 x RS232, 3 x RS485, 2 x CAN